She saw Kluster turn around and saw the bot who all were aiming there 
weapons at.  She transformed back to lioness mode and stood with her 
claws ready.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Firearm/Kluster::
> 
> "Hey, Kluster!" Firearm says loudly, walking up to Kluster, "The 
Preds ran 
> off. Didn't even give us time to get warmed up!"
> 
> Kluster nods, looking around. His eyes narrow as he sees Deemos 
near the 
> ship. He motions to Firearm, the two Maximals walking over to 
Deemos, their 
> guns ready.
> 
> "May we help you?" Kluster asks.
